{
  "stem": "9156.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I will not go into all the details, but at Passover, it was horrible because we had to change everything and we worked very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everything that was in the store had to be taken out, and only matzo was put in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everything was cleaned out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we children, at that time, had to work so hard because our clients that were richer Jews in the neighborhood would never come and pick up anything.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to carry odd things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was known as a schlepper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "S-C-H-L-E-P-P-E-R.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could carry, from early on, everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My hands were strong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it was very hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at night, we had to prepare for the next day, to get things together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I, I still remember falling asleep on the toilet because I was so tired.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But this is later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, I mean maybe perhaps 12 years old, what I'm just talking about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But you asked about the religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yes, my-- both parents were practicing, but Mother was much more, what I call today, reasonable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "For instance, I remember that I hated matzo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I just didn't like that stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my father wouldn't allow anything, and I still remember my mother once secretly putting a little piece of bread in my hand and say, go and hide it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Eat it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I wasn't eating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was a very sickly child-- nobody will believe that-- and really thin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she must have been worried, but she did that for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was much more at ease, I always felt, with her religion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If she felt something had to be done, it had to be done even-- by my father would not know about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
